<p>Things change in v5: The suffixes ‚ÄúDeterministic‚Äù and ‚ÄúNoFrameskip‚Äù are no longer available. Instead, you must specify the
environment configuration via arguments passed to <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">gym.make</code>. Moreover, the v5 environments
are in the ‚ÄúALE‚Äù namespace. The suffix ‚Äú-ram‚Äù is still available. Thus, we get the following table:</p>

